    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $120 (commercial tier, applied to outdoor work), waived with repair. OEM Hestan parts only. We source through Hestan Commercial customer care or the authorized dealer network. Hestan parts are not commodity, no aftermarket of consequence.</p>

