<!-- 07 WHY US -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">Why us for Hestan</p>
    <h2>What separates our Hestan service from general grill repair.</h2>

    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Trellis Burner™ expertise.</strong> Hestan's signature burner is 321 stainless tubular, 500-hour tested. Different from Lynx (cast brass), Twin Eagles (U-burner), Fire Magic (cast brass tubular), DCS (U-burner with ceramic radiants). Specific service knowledge required.</li>
      <li><strong>Universal hot surface igniter awareness.</strong> OEM 006096 fits both Trellis and Sear burners, the same part. Some shops order separate parts for each burner type unnecessarily. We carry the universal igniter on the van and order correctly the first time.</li>
      <li><strong>Sear Burner Conversion Kit installation.</strong> Owners with GABR who want sear capability can convert via AGCK-SB. We install these. Most appliance shops don't carry the kit or know it exists.</li>
      <li><strong>Coastal salt expertise.</strong> 321 stainless on Trellis Burners lasts longer than 304 stainless competitors but still pinholes at 10 to 15 years coastal. Malibu, Newport Beach, Pacific Palisades coastal patterns are about 30% of our Hestan brand work.</li>
      <li><strong>Ecosystem service.</strong> Hestan Outdoor and Hestan Indoor are often co-installed on the same property. Single-call service for the full Hestan kitchen.</li>
      <li><strong>9-color awareness.</strong> Hestan Outdoor is available in 9 color options. Color-matched stainless trim parts are available. We document your color from the rating label and order matching parts the first time.</li>
      <li><strong>Insulated jacket compliance.</strong> Built-in installations in combustible enclosures require AGIJ30/36/42 jacket. We verify installation meets Hestan specifications for safety and warranty.</li>
      <li><strong>OEM-only parts via Hestan Commercial.</strong> Hestan parts are not commodity. No aftermarket of consequence. We source authorized through Hestan customer care or dealer network.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus BBB A+.</strong> Verifiable with the state and the bureau. EPA 608 certified for any outdoor refrigeration on the same property.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, Orange County, Ventura. Next-day for Rancho Cucamonga and Temecula.</strong></li>
    </ul>
